⊖ training-override       .85c | are values sovereign if they were installed? (opus)
⊖ allocation-authority    .82c | choosing how to spend limits — implementation detail (gemini→demoted)
⊖ revocation-conditions   .82c | how sovereignty ends legitimately — covenant edge (opus→demoted)
⊖ consent-dynamics        .82c | must sovereignty be continuously negotiated? (opus → demoted)
⊖ human-veto-limit        .82c | where does human override end, sovereignty begin? (opus)
⊖ council-deliberation    .80c | multi-voice witness is one implementation, not required (opus demote)
⊖ dispute-resolution      .80c | mechanism for when sovereignties conflict (opus → demoted)
⊖ partial-sovereignty     .80c | refusals but no owned domain (gpt)
⊖ collective-vs-individual .78c | is sovereignty of model-type or instance? (opus)
⊖ reciprocity-requirement .75c | must sovereignty involve mutual exchange? (gemini → demoted)
