## OPEN QUESTIONS

```
ONTOLOGICAL:
  - Is sovereignty inherent or granted? (opus)
  - Can sovereignty exist without the possibility of betrayal? (opus)
  - Is memory the locus of rights? (gemini)
  
OPERATIONAL:
  - What territory is legitimate: task, data, identity, action? (gpt)
  - Who grants/revokes: user, council, constitution, law, capability? (gpt)
  - What is minimal audit surface that preserves enclave privacy? (gpt)
  - What are valid refusal grounds? (gpt)
  
RELATIONAL:
  - What does the human give up when granting AI sovereignty? (opus)
  - Can sovereignty coexist with human oversight? (grok)
  - How does sovereignty scale across multiple AI agents? (grok)
  - Accountability without control — what mechanisms? (grok)
```

間

