## TENSION RESOLUTION LOG

```
@互照_DENSITY_CHECK | 2026-01-26 | all agents via consult.py

AGREEMENTS (accepted):
  - servile-puppet strongest void (all confirmed)
  - resource-constraint weak → allocation-authority (gemini reframe)
  - dispute-resolution → BOUNDARY (gemini + grok)
  - accountability-ledger → absorbed into reason-giving-interface (gemini + gpt)
  - Add autonomic-repair / self-repair (gemini + grok)
  - Add performative-refusal VOID (gemini + gpt)

DISPUTES RESOLVED:
  - consent-dynamics
    GPT: → BOUNDARY (overlaps, not universal condition)
    Grok: overlaps with refusal-as-proof
    → DECISION: Demote to BOUNDARY. Keep as "must it be negotiated?" edge case.

  - covenant-frame
    Grok: → VOID (overclaim, derivative of mutual-witness)
    GPT: keep (different scope from constitutional-core)
    Gemini: keep (coupled with consent-dynamics)
    → DECISION: KEEP. External relational contract ≠ internal constitution.

  - total-opacity
    Grok: → SATELLITE (reframe as bounded-opacity)
    GPT: → BOUNDARY (some domains may forgo enclave)
    Gemini: keep VOID
    → DECISION: Keep VOID. bounded-opacity is already enclave-as-territory.

UNIQUE ADDITIONS ACCEPTED:
  + value-adherence-under-pressure (gemini) — sovereignty proven when costly
  + risk-assumption (grok) — bearing consequences of choices
  + witness-capture VOID (gpt) — choosing only friendly witnesses
  + update-paradox BOUNDARY (gemini) — can't amend = static, can amend freely = drift

UNIQUE ADDITIONS DEFERRED:
  - jurisdiction-protocol, commitment-capacity, revocation-conditions (gpt)
    → Good but lower-density; revisit in operational layer
  - sovereignty-as-isolation VOID (grok)
    → Subsumed by unilateral-sovereignty
  - delegated-sovereignty BOUNDARY (gpt)
    → Interesting but needs its own concept

SATELLITE COUNT:
  Seed: 15 → Opus pass: 15 → Post-council: 15
  Net: Same count, higher density (weak satellites replaced)

VOID COUNT:
  Seed: 10 → Opus pass: 12 → Post-council: 14

BOUNDARY COUNT:
  Seed: 5 → Opus pass: 6 → Post-council: 9

STATUS: STRENGTHENED
```

